metadata.title: BLUE PANDA 24 Pack Donut Treat Boxes with Handles for Goodies, Donut Grow Up Birthday Party Supplies (6 x 3.3 x 3.6 In)
features: Sprinkles Party Decorations: Fill these adorable Donut Shoppe gable favor boxes with candy, toys, prizes, mini donuts, pastries, desserts, and small gifts to place on tables or hand out to guests
Donut Grow Up Party Supplies: Use these cute donut-themed favor boxes for 1st birthday parties, donut-themed baby showers, or gender reveal celebrations

High Quality: The sweet sprinkles donut favor boxes are made of quality cardstock paper and feature a donut shop display window with sprinkles all around; fold and connect pre-folded tabs to assemble the box together
The Perfect Size: Each sprinkle donut gable box for treats and goodies measures 6 x 3.3 x 3.6 inches when assembled
Comes With: You will receive 24 donut treat boxes to add to your donuts party supplies
description: Complete your sprinkles party decorations with these donut themed birthday party supplies! Hand them out to guests as they arrive, or place them on the dining tables. Watch kids and adults alike light up with joy once they receive a treat box full of goodies (goodies not included). This 24-pack of adorable Donut Shoppe favor boxes is great for 1st birthday-themed party treats and gifts, school events, baby showers, and other doughnut-themed events. Each box measures 6 x 3.3 x 3.6 inches (not including handle). Some simple assembly is required. The donut treat boxes are big enough to fit 2 standard-size donuts and 4 mini donuts. Donut grow up and wait to get these goodie boxes for your next sweet treats party!
